  • Packages that use Catalano.MachineLearning 
    Package Description
    Catalano.MachineLearning
    The Catalano.MachineLearning namespace contains interfaces and classes for different algorithms of machine learning.

    The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification namespace contains interfaces and classes for classifications.
    Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees
    The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees namespace contains decision trees algorithms.
    Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees.Learning
    The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.DecisionTrees.Learning namespace contains decision trees learning algorithms.
    Catalano.MachineLearning.Performance
    The Catalano.MachineLearning.Performance namespace contains interfaces and classes for performance measure classification.
    Catalano.MachineLearning.Regression.RegressionTrees
    The Catalano.MachineLearning.Classification.RegressionTrees namespace contains regression trees algorithms.
